programme.desc: Emmy award winner for "Outstanding Talk Show" this chat-fest features a team of dynamic women of different ages, experiences and backgrounds discussing the most topical events of the day. يتضمن هذا البرنامج الحواري الفائز بجائزة إيمي مجموعة من النساء من أعمار وتجارب وخلفيات مختلفة حيث يتناقشن في أهم الأحداث التي تحصل.

ماغنوم بي. آي.
programme.desc: While Magnum helps out his friend Russell Harlan and temporarily works as the head of a hotel's security, he investigates the death of a guest who was thrown from her room's balcony while working on a secret investigation of her own. بينما يساعد ماغنوم صديقه راسل هارلان ويعمل مؤقتًا كرئيس لأمن الفندق ، فإنه يحقق في وفاة نزيلة ألقيت من شرفة غرفتها أثناء عمله في تحقيق سري خاص بها.

programme.title: Good Trouble

programme.desc: The Coterie attends Trap Heals while facing tough decisions. Malika feels the weight of her family's and Isaac's anxiety. Callie deals with a moral dilemma. programme.title: Beecham House

programme.desc: John has spent several days and nights in his cell and has finally worked out who betrayed him. programme.title: Future Man

programme.title: Silicon Valley
سيليكون فالي
programme.desc: The launch of PiperNet finds Monica suspicious of an early success, and the team must race against the clock as their future is threatened. programme.title: Dollface

programme.desc: Jules pretends to be over her breakup with Jeremy at his sister's bachelorette party.
